---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="px-6 py-14 hairline-top">
  <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <img src="/icon-192.png" alt="THREADLINE" class="w-6 h-6 rounded-[6px]" />
          <span class="font-display text-[13px] font-bold tracking-tight">
            THREAD<span class="text-gradient">LINE</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[12px] leading-relaxed max-w-[240px]" style="color: hsl(255,8%,45%);">
          Визуальное пространство для идей, файлов, референсов и проектов — от ремонта квартиры до SaaS-системы.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-[10.5px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: hsl(255,8%,40%);">Продукт</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[12.5px]" style="color: hsl(255,8%,60%);">
          <li><a href="#features" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Фичи</a></li>
          <li><a href="#how" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Как это работает</a></li>
          <li><a href="#pricing" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Тарифы</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://threadline.tigerapps.pro/login" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">API для агентов</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Блог</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-[10.5px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: hsl(255,8%,40%);">Ресурсы</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[12.5px]" style="color: hsl(255,8%,60%);">
          <li><a href="/docs" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Документация</a></li>
          <li><a href="/changelog" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Changelog</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:support@threadline.tigerapps.pro" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Поддержка</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-[10.5px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: hsl(255,8%,40%);">Юридическое</div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[12.5px]" style="color: hsl(255,8%,60%);">
          <li><a href="/legal/terms" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Terms of Service</a></li>
          <li><a href="/legal/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/legal/cookies" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cookie Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/legal/refunds" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Refund Policy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[11.5px] pt-6 hairline-top" style="color: hsl(255,8%,40%);">
      <div>© {year} THREADLINE. Все права защищены.</div>
      <div>Сделано в команде tigerapps</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
